    "description": "一个女人独自一人在房子里。一个谜和一个爱情故事。探索现在，揭开过去。一个关于爱情、遗失、美好的短篇小说。一个记忆混乱、不断消逝的叙事探索游戏。一个关于痴呆症的故事。当你无法坚持所做的事情或忘记所爱之人时会发生什么呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/f00083f0bc15aa075fe19abaf4ed03c3.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=403 /></span><br><br><i>“这是哪？……我来这里干什么？”</i><br><br>回响的钢琴哀曲。逾期2年的日历。弥漫陈旧气味的房子。一个独自在她房子里的女人，她有一个谜......<br><br>你是Sunita － 一个患有早发性痴呆症的女性。 当你在一个个房间徘徊时，你会发现一件件神秘的物品，每件物品都承载着短暂而零散的记忆。 通过查看褪色的明信片，充滿着潦草笔记的便条，照片以及更多其他内容，你可以回忆Sunita的过去，拼凑她的生活故事并了解她的现在。<br><br>《回忆满屋》是3-Fold Games制作的一个故事丰富和第一人称视角探索的游戏。精致，动容且有感染力，这个游戏反映了痴呆症对情感的影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/088d3d873a209a13bd8caa12f9049ffd.poster.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/088d3d873a209a13bd8caa12f9049ffd.webm?t=1699887354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/088d3d873a209a13bd8caa12f9049ffd.mp4?t=1699887354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/91e870002b5e3ff8d48681d253624907.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>短小精悍：</strong> 《回忆满屋》是一款由3-Fold Games制作的叙事类游戏。它的平均游戏时长为1小时，确保玩家得到一气呵成的游戏体验。<br></li><li><strong>剧情丰富：</strong> Sunita的房子是一个掩藏着许多褪色的记忆的宝库。《回忆满屋》的游戏世界表现力出众，游戏细节与背景故事丰富，将带你踏上一段令人印象深刻的情感之旅。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/6267ce24f9d2575e67e8f218503b1335.poster.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/6267ce24f9d2575e67e8f218503b1335.webm?t=1699887354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/6267ce24f9d2575e67e8f218503b1335.mp4?t=1699887354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>配音精湛：</strong> 配音演员的专业配音为游戏增添了活力，用声音为主角Sunita和她的记忆注入了灵魂。（包括Anjali Kunapaneni和Bushra Laskar）<br></li><li><strong>原创音乐：</strong> 作曲家Dave Tucker的原创音乐将引导你去感受Sunita的内在与外在世界，并在优雅的钢琴旋律中重拾那段如风般的记忆。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/61dc83b48925c6a73932e1a58ccde0f8.poster.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/61dc83b48925c6a73932e1a58ccde0f8.webm?t=1699887354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/61dc83b48925c6a73932e1a58ccde0f8.mp4?t=1699887354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/745d52454df60cb78c34e2f7ecc8ae0d.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br><i>“除了Sunita这个名字外，我们还想从其他的方面显现她的印度身份。所以，我用Galaxy手机上的一个小软件作了这幅画，[……]所以这是我的敬意，一份微不足道的敬意——致一位了不起的印度女画家[……] 她就是Amrita Sher-Gil。”</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/fca0bc80cb0aaae2257672c26b14de48.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>《回忆满屋》的诞生源自于一条开发者的评论，你可以从游戏的加载屏幕上激活它。当你在探索Sunita的房间时，你可以聆听游戏开发者发人深省的访谈，分析他们的创造过程，揭露秘密等等。此功能目前只有英文版本。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/ec4bf882e57242fd1c6475f83c0a414b.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/d9ce296061aa62404af78abcc3d15249.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=403 /></span><br><br>3-Fold Games由开发者Claire Morwood和Chella Ramanan建立，公司虽小，但功能强大。他们致力于从之前未被充分代表的群体角度去讲述不同的故事，富有创造性的二人组将创造游戏作为使命，为那些经常被排除在游戏叙述之外的个人和群体提供发言权。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126600/extras/601b547ed97e60fc9f5e57b193ebd772.avif?t=1699887354\" width=600 height=165 /></span>",
